attributes.title: Play, You Fools! - Super Princess Rescue Quest RPG Ep 1
attributes.caption: "He puts Pogo up his butt."
attributes.description:
A band of half-pint sized heroes face fierce foes, perilous puzzles, and a comical cast of characters as they travel far and wide to save the heir to the throne. But does this group of unlikely adventurers have what it takes? Find out in this season of Must Be Dice: Super Princess Rescue Quest! It's just like all your favorite fantasy TV shows minus the rings, towers, thrones, returned kings, wheels, songs, ice, or fire.
